Package com.intellij.psi.formatter.java.wrap.impl

Class JavaChildBlockWrapFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.psi.formatter.java.wrap.impl.JavaChildBlockWrapFactory

  • public class JavaChildBlockWrapFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates algorithm of construction wraps for sub-blocks of particular block taking into consideration current formatting settings.

    Thread-safe.

      • create

        public Wrap create(ASTBlock block,
                   CommonCodeStyleSettings settings,
                   ReservedWrapsProvider reservedWrapsProvider)
        Creates wrap to be used with the children blocks of the the given block.
        Parameters:
        block - target block which sub-blocks should use wrap created by the current method
        settings - code formatting settings to consider during wrap construction
        reservedWrapsProvider - reserved 'element type -> wrap instance' mappings provider. Note: this argument is considered to be a part of legacy heritage and is intended to be removed as soon as formatting code refactoring is done
        Returns:
        wrap to use for the sub-blocks of the given block
